        <h1>GuideMe</h1>
        <p>A free app that conects you with locals when you are traveling. Share the experiences that only a local would know about!</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#" role="button">Sign in with Facebook &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
